    "is_free": true,
    "description": "在试玩版中，你将可以体验到部分卡牌角色和组合效果；欢迎关注本游戏的正式版发布以获得更完整的体验~很快就和大家见面！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168860/extras/bd29891344c5d1afe55079dd3e9db348.avif?t=1748315733\" width=610 height=100 /></span><br>朝廷拥有丰富多样的卡牌，牌组的搭配可得到不同的效果。皇上需要在每个回合中选择卡牌，拨出银两下发政令、增设武器、置办部门......大力发展商农，带领王朝成为一方富饶；还是招兵买马，打造一支令敌人闻风丧胆的军队？皇上请下令！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168860/extras/2d604eeaf70053306f41322e4cb7f384.poster.avif?t=1748315733\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168860/extras/2d604eeaf70053306f41322e4cb7f384.webm?t=1748315733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168860/extras/f26d3dd4101f2b0790574171146389d2.avif?t=1748315733\" width=610 height=100 /></span><br>天有不测风云，王朝也会遭遇许多变数。或许是虎视眈眈的叛军来袭，或许是鼠疫蝗灾害民。皇上需要凭借英明才智抵御灾患、消灭叛军，庇护子民。倘若安然度过，定必万世敬仰，流芳百世！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168860/extras/67be3f81158d649de8654c541e352323.poster.avif?t=1748315733\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168860/extras/67be3f81158d649de8654c541e352323.webm?t=1748315733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168860/extras/0e39b43e5dc114243840b94d940767d6.avif?t=1748315733\" width=610 height=100 /></span><br>如要国家富庶，击退外敌，离不开合理的政策。布政司、官盐制、坑儒令、安民书、典民令、增税、军屯制、农具改良等等政策各有千秋。皇上请合理下旨政策，以天子之福相润泽天下。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168860/extras/ae1a3f41b83090dff36301264b6b9359.poster.avif?t=1748315733\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168860/extras/ae1a3f41b83090dff36301264b6b9359.webm?t=1748315733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168860/extras/aee32e662ef127c049e17a024a4389f4.avif?t=1748315733\" width=610 height=100 /></span><br>农民、商贾、铁匠各司其职，巡抚、县令、州使辅佐朝政，捕快、士兵、弩手保卫安宁。人生百态，行业众多，望皇上选择合适的卡牌组合，任人唯贤，兴国邦，安天下。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168860/extras/c0e4619e089e81c6b245ecc9102f1bdc.poster.avif?t=1748315733\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168860/extras/c0e4619e089e81c6b245ecc9102f1bdc.webm?t=1748315733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168860/extras/57c348c6cdc97e79e579a16e2871046d.webp?t=1748315733\" width=610 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168860/extras/dbe1a188b572cf781cb0751519a6dd64.avif?t=1748315733\" width=610 height=75 /></span>",
